<v-dialog
  v-model="value"
  max-width="300"
>
  <v-card>
    <v-card-title class="headline">{{$t('alert.confirm')}}</v-card-title>
    <v-card-text>
      {{$t('alert.confirm_delete')}}
    </v-card-text>
    <v-card-actions>
      <v-spacer></v-spacer>
      <v-btn
        color="green darken-1"
        flat="flat"
        @click="accept()"
      >
        {{$t('alert.accept')}}
      </v-btn>

      <v-btn
        color="red darken-1"
        flat="flat"
        @click="cancel()"
      >
        {{$t('alert.donot')}}
      </v-btn>
    </v-card-actions>
  </v-card>
</v-dialog>
